  "text": "Then by using equation [CITATION_1] and its derivative to eliminate x and x from equation (5), upon expanding the term (1 \u2212 \u03bb 2 y 2 ) 1/2 into a power series and noting that (\u03bb 2 y 2 ) < l, equation (5) becomes when the nonlinear terms retained up to fourth order;",
